1. *Dijete* se igralo sa loptom. (The child was playing with the ball.)
2. Ono je *dijete* koje voli da se igra. (It is a child who likes to play.)
3. *Dijete* je preskočilo ogradu. (The child jumped over the fence.)
4. Ono je *dijetetu* dalo slatkiš. (It gave the child a candy.)
5. *Dijetu* je poslao poklon. (He sent a gift to the child.)
6. Ona je svoje *dijete* vodila u park. (She took her child to the park.)
7. Ona je čuvala svoje *dijete*. (She was taking care of her child.)
8. On je svoje *dijete* držao za ruku. (He held his child by the hand.)